        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="header" id="heading-one">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#discipline-accordion-investment-and-risk-management" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="discipline-accordion-investment-and-risk-management">
                    <h3>Investment and Risk Management</h3>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="discipline-accordion-investment-and-risk-management" class="collapse " data-parent="#disciplines-accordion">
                <div class="container mb-3">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 mb-2">
                            <p>Ideal for careers in investment fields, where you’ll analyze risk in financial markets and asset trading. You could manage investment portfolios, make acquisition decisions or act as risk advisor for banks or global companies.</p>

                            <p><strong>Did you know?</strong></p>
<p>You can learn investing in one of the largest academic trading rooms in the US, identical to those used by leading financial institutions, at Hofstra University in New York.</p>

                        </div>
